  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the impact of using a computerized decision program on the adequacy of the
      perioperative antimicrobial prophylaxis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Adequacy rate of surgical antimicrobial prophylaxis, helped by a computerized decision
      support system, according to the internal guidelines considering the aspects: drug choice,
      dosing, timing, and re-dosing
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
